\leq ||\mathbf{x} - \mathbf{w}|| +  ||\mathbf{z} - \mathbf{y}||
|x \cdot y - x \cdot z| = |x \cdot (y -z)| \leq \|x\| \|y-z\| \leq \|x\| (\|y\|+\|z\|) = 2 (3+4)
